  "Description": {
    "English": "A metal 'egg' capsule, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>A regular electronic beeping can be heard from within the egg, soft and somehow reassuring.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within is programmed to be <span class=\"name name-special\">meticulous</span> and <span class=\"name name-special\">dependable</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一个金属胶囊“蛋”，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已经准备好孵化！</span><br><br>能够听见蛋壳内正在持续不断发出电子设备的哔哔声，柔和的声响让人感到十分宁静。<br><br>根据扫描结果显示，里面的存在已经被编入<span class=\"name name-special\">细致</span>以及<span class=\"name name-special\">可靠</span>的程序。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一個金屬「蛋」膠囊，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">即將孵化！</span><br><br>可以從蛋裡面聽到規律的電子嗶嗶聲，柔和且奇妙地令人感到安心。<br><br>掃描結果顯示，該生物經程序設計，具有以下形容地大小及特徵：<span class=\"name name-special\">細心</span>且<span class=\"name name-special\">值得信賴</span>。"
  },
